## Audit / freeze note

This artifact is frozen at render time. The rendered HTML reads the local copy of `colors_and_type.css` synced into the artifact bundle, not a live upstream URL. To re-render against newer upstream tokens, re-sync the local mirror, record a new commit SHA, and regenerate. The previous artifact remains valid for audit at its recorded SHA.
